hadiths[13]{hadithnumber,text}:
1067,Makka main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sura Najm ki tilawat ki aur sajda tilawat kya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jitney aadmi they ( musalman aur kaafir ( un sab ne bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath sajda kya albatta aik boodha shakhs ( Umayya-bin-Khalaf ( apne hath mein kankari ya mitti utha kar apni peshani tak ley gaya aur kaha mere liye yahi kafi hai maine dekha ke baad mein wo boodha haalate-kufr mein hi maara gaya.
1068,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Juma ke din fajr ki Namaz main ( الم تنزيل‏ السجدة) aur Sura Dahar padha kartey they.
1069,sura Swaad ka sajda kuchh taakidi sajdon mein se nahi hai aur maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko sajda kartey huey dekha.
1070,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sura Najm ki tilawat ki aur is mein sajda kya us waqt qaum ka koi fard ( musalman aur kaafir ( bhi aisa na tha jisne sajda na kya ho. albatta aik shakhs ( Umayya-bin-Khalaf ( ne hath mein kankari ya mitti lekar apne chehre tak uthai aur kaha ke mere liye yahi kafi hai. Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke baad mein maine dekha ke wo kufr ki haalat hi mein qatl hua.
1071,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sura Najm mein sajda kya to muslmaanon, mushrikon aur jinnon aur insanon sab ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath sajda kya. us hadis ki riwayat Ibrahim bin tahmaan ne bhi Ayub sakhtiyan se ki hai."
1072,unhon-ne-Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) se sawal kya. aap ne yaqin ke sath is baat ka izhar kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney sura Najm ki tilawat aap ne ki thi aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usmein sajda nahi kya.
1073,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney sura Najm ki tilawat ki aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usmein sajda nahi kya.
1074,maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko sura ( إذا السماء انشقت‏ ( padhtey dekha. aap ne usmein sajda kya maine kaha ke aey Abu-Hurera ! kya maine aapko sajda kartey huey nahi dekha hai. aap ne kaha ke agar main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko sajda kartey na dekhta to main bhi na karta.
1075,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamari maujoodgii mein aayate-sajda padhtey aur sajda kartey to ham bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ( hujoom ki wjah se) is tarah sajda kartey ke peshani rakhney ki jagah bhi na miltii jis par sajda kartey.
1076,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aayate-sajda ki tilawat agar hamari maujoodgii mein kartey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ham bhi sajda kartey they. us waqt itni bheed ho jati ke sajde ke liye peshani rakhney ki jagah na miltii jis par sajda karne wala sajda kar sakey.
1077,Rabee bahut achchhey logon mein se they Rabee ne wo haal bayan kya jo Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ki majlis mein unhon-ne dekha. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Juma ke din member par sura Nahal padhi jab sajde ki aayat ( ‏‏‏‏ولله يسجد ما في السمٰوٰت ( Mina aakhir tak pahunchey to member par se utrey aur sajda kya to logon ne bhi unke sath sajda kya. doosrey Juma ko phir yahi sura padhi jab sajde ki aayat par pahunchey to kehney lagey logo! ham sajde ki aayat padhtey chaley jatey hain phir jo koi sajda karey usne achchha kya aur jo koi na karey to is par kuchh gunah nahi aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne sajda nahi kya aur Naafe ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se naql kya ke Allah Taala ne sajda tilawat farz nahi kya hamari khushi par rakha.
1078,maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath namaaze-ishaa padhi. aap ne ( إذا السماء انشقت‏ ( ki tilawat ki aur sajda kya. maine arz kya ke aap ne ye kya kya? unhon-ne iska jawab diya ke maine usmein abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein sajda kya tha aur hamesha sajda karta rahunga yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ja miloon.
1079,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi aisi sura ki tilawat kartey jis mein sajda hota, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajda kartey aur ham bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath sajda kartey yahan tak ke ham mein kisi ko apni peshani rakhney ki jagah na miltii. (ma'loom hua ke aisi haalat mein sajda na kya jaey to koi harj nahi hai) ( والله أعلم ( ."
